API Endpoints
http://localhost:8080/graphql

Queries

current

Response

Returns a CurrentUser

Example

Query
query current {
  current {
    id
    name
    lastName
    login
    realmId
    groups
    roles
  }
}
Response
{
  "data": {
    "current": {
      "id": "xyz789",
      "name": "abc123",
      "lastName": "abc123",
      "login": "abc123",
      "realmId": 987,
      "groups": ["abc123"],
      "roles": ["abc123"]
    }
  }
}

Queries

group

Response

Returns a Group

Arguments
Name Description
id - StringExpression
name - StringExpression
description - StringExpression
path - StringExpression
deep - IntExpression
parentId - StringExpression
parent - GroupExpression
subGroups - GroupExpression
users - UserExpression
roles - RoleExpression
realm - RealmExpression
includeDeprecated - Boolean Default = false
version - IntExpression
realmId - IntExpression
createUserId - StringExpression
createTime - StringExpression
updateUserId - StringExpression
updateTime - StringExpression
createGroupId - StringExpression
groupUserRelation - GroupUserRelationExpression
groupRoleRelation - GroupRoleRelationExpression
groupBy - [String!]
not - Boolean Default = false
cond - Conditional Default = "AND"
exs - [GroupExpression]

Example

Query
query group(
  $id: StringExpression,
  $name: StringExpression,
  $description: StringExpression,
  $path: StringExpression,
  $deep: IntExpression,
  $parentId: StringExpression,
  $parent: GroupExpression,
  $subGroups: GroupExpression,
  $users: UserExpression,
  $roles: RoleExpression,
  $realm: RealmExpression,
  $includeDeprecated: Boolean,
  $version: IntExpression,
  $realmId: IntExpression,
  $createUserId: StringExpression,
  $createTime: StringExpression,
  $updateUserId: StringExpression,
  $updateTime: StringExpression,
  $createGroupId: StringExpression,
  $groupUserRelation: GroupUserRelationExpression,
  $groupRoleRelation: GroupRoleRelationExpression,
  $groupBy: [String!],
  $not: Boolean,
  $cond: Conditional,
  $exs: [GroupExpression]
) {
  group(
    id: $id,
    name: $name,
    description: $description,
    path: $path,
    deep: $deep,
    parentId: $parentId,
    parent: $parent,
    subGroups: $subGroups,
    users: $users,
    roles: $roles,
    realm: $realm,
    includeDeprecated: $includeDeprecated,
    version: $version,
    realmId: $realmId,
    createUserId: $createUserId,
    createTime: $createTime,
    updateUserId: $updateUserId,
    updateTime: $updateTime,
    createGroupId: $createGroupId,
    groupUserRelation: $groupUserRelation,
    groupRoleRelation: $groupRoleRelation,
    groupBy: $groupBy,
    not: $not,
    cond: $cond,
    exs: $exs
  ) {
    id
    name
    description
    path
    deep
    parentId
    parent {
      ...GroupFragment
    }
    subGroups {
      ...GroupFragment
    }
    users {
      ...UserFragment
    }
    roles {
      ...RoleFragment
    }
    realm {
      ...RealmFragment
    }
    isDeprecated
    version
    realmId
    createUserId
    createTime
    updateUserId
    updateTime
    createGroupId
    groupUserRelation {
      ...GroupUserRelationFragment
    }
    groupRoleRelation {
      ...GroupRoleRelationFragment
    }
    subGroupsAggregate {
      ...GroupFragment
    }
    subGroupsConnection {
      ...GroupConnectionFragment
    }
    usersAggregate {
      ...UserFragment
    }
    usersConnection {
      ...UserConnectionFragment
    }
    rolesAggregate {
      ...RoleFragment
    }
    rolesConnection {
      ...RoleConnectionFragment
    }
    groupUserRelationAggregate {
      ...GroupUserRelationFragment
    }
    groupUserRelationConnection {
      ...GroupUserRelationConnectionFragment
    }
    groupRoleRelationAggregate {
      ...GroupRoleRelationFragment
    }
    groupRoleRelationConnection {
      ...GroupRoleRelationConnectionFragment
    }
    idCount
    idMax
    idMin
    nameCount
    nameMax
    nameMin
    descriptionCount
    descriptionMax
    descriptionMin
    pathCount
    pathMax
    pathMin
    parentIdCount
    parentIdMax
    parentIdMin
    deepCount
    deepSum
    deepAvg
    deepMax
    deepMin
    syncGroupPolicy
  }
}

groupConnection

Response

Returns a GroupConnection

Arguments
Name Description
id - StringExpression
name - StringExpression
description - StringExpression
path - StringExpression
deep - IntExpression
parentId - StringExpression
parent - GroupExpression
subGroups - GroupExpression
users - UserExpression
roles - RoleExpression
realm - RealmExpression
includeDeprecated - Boolean Default = false
version - IntExpression
realmId - IntExpression
createUserId - StringExpression
createTime - StringExpression
updateUserId - StringExpression
updateTime - StringExpression
createGroupId - StringExpression
groupUserRelation - GroupUserRelationExpression
groupRoleRelation - GroupRoleRelationExpression
orderBy - GroupOrderBy
groupBy - [String!]
not - Boolean Default = false
cond - Conditional Default = "AND"
exs - [GroupExpression]
first - Int
last - Int
offset - Int
after - ID
before - ID

Example

Query
query groupConnection(
  $id: StringExpression,
  $name: StringExpression,
  $description: StringExpression,
  $path: StringExpression,
  $deep: IntExpression,
  $parentId: StringExpression,
  $parent: GroupExpression,
  $subGroups: GroupExpression,
  $users: UserExpression,
  $roles: RoleExpression,
  $realm: RealmExpression,
  $includeDeprecated: Boolean,
  $version: IntExpression,
  $realmId: IntExpression,
  $createUserId: StringExpression,
  $createTime: StringExpression,
  $updateUserId: StringExpression,
  $updateTime: StringExpression,
  $createGroupId: StringExpression,
  $groupUserRelation: GroupUserRelationExpression,
  $groupRoleRelation: GroupRoleRelationExpression,
  $orderBy: GroupOrderBy,
  $groupBy: [String!],
  $not: Boolean,
  $cond: Conditional,
  $exs: [GroupExpression],
  $first: Int,
  $last: Int,
  $offset: Int,
  $after: ID,
  $before: ID
) {
  groupConnection(
    id: $id,
    name: $name,
    description: $description,
    path: $path,
    deep: $deep,
    parentId: $parentId,
    parent: $parent,
    subGroups: $subGroups,
    users: $users,
    roles: $roles,
    realm: $realm,
    includeDeprecated: $includeDeprecated,
    version: $version,
    realmId: $realmId,
    createUserId: $createUserId,
    createTime: $createTime,
    updateUserId: $updateUserId,
    updateTime: $updateTime,
    createGroupId: $createGroupId,
    groupUserRelation: $groupUserRelation,
    groupRoleRelation: $groupRoleRelation,
    orderBy: $orderBy,
    groupBy: $groupBy,
    not: $not,
    cond: $cond,
    exs: $exs,
    first: $first,
    last: $last,
    offset: $offset,
    after: $after,
    before: $before
  ) {
    totalCount
    pageInfo {
      ...PageInfoFragment
    }
    edges {
      ...GroupEdgeFragment
    }
  }
}

  "name": StringExpression,

Example

Query
query groupRoleRelation(
  $id: StringExpression,
  $roleRef: StringExpression,
  $role: RoleExpression,
  $groupRef: StringExpression,
  $group: GroupExpression,
  $includeDeprecated: Boolean,
  $version: IntExpression,
  $realmId: IntExpression,
  $createUserId: StringExpression,
  $createTime: StringExpression,
  $updateUserId: StringExpression,
  $updateTime: StringExpression,
  $createGroupId: StringExpression,
  $groupBy: [String!],
  $not: Boolean,
  $cond: Conditional,
  $exs: [GroupRoleRelationExpression]
) {
  groupRoleRelation(
    id: $id,
    roleRef: $roleRef,
    role: $role,
    groupRef: $groupRef,
    group: $group,
    includeDeprecated: $includeDeprecated,
    version: $version,
    realmId: $realmId,
    createUserId: $createUserId,
    createTime: $createTime,
    updateUserId: $updateUserId,
    updateTime: $updateTime,
    createGroupId: $createGroupId,
    groupBy: $groupBy,
    not: $not,
    cond: $cond,
    exs: $exs
  ) {
    id
    roleRef
    role {
      ...RoleFragment
    }
    groupRef
    group {
      ...GroupFragment
    }
    isDeprecated
    version
    realmId
    createUserId
    createTime
    updateUserId
    updateTime
    createGroupId
    idCount
    idMax
    idMin
    roleRefCount
    roleRefMax
    roleRefMin
    groupRefCount
    groupRefMax
    groupRefMin
  }

    id: $id,

    subGroups: $subGroups,
